OL,3,CWhat do we know about Labour's
OL,4,Cworkers' rights legislation?
OL,6,FThe bill will set out 'day one rights'
OL,7,Ffor workers - but ITV News understands
OL,8,Fthat they will not come into play
OL,9,Funtil Autumn 2026.
OL,11,FEmployers at the meeting pressed
OL,12,FRayner to set out what a probation
OL,13,Fperiod would look like, to which she
OL,14,Fresponded that there would be a
OL,15,F"consultation" on what she hoped was a
OL,16,F"reasonable balance". Sources have
OL,17,Fsuggested that a probation period is
OL,18,Flikely to stretch from six to nine
OL,19,Fmonths.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
