OL,3,CWhat do we know about Labour's
OL,4,Cworkers' rights legislation?
OL,6,FHowever, in a significant shift from
OL,7,Fthe current situation, workers would
OL,8,Fstill have the rights listed from
OL,9,Ftheir first day of work - including
OL,10,Fthe right to avoid 'unfair dismissal'.
OL,11,FCurrently, workers may not qualify for
OL,12,Fthat for up to two years.
OL,14,FBosses at the meeting raised questions
OL,15,Fover the length of the probation
OL,16,Fperiod.
OL,18,FBut questions have also been asked
OL,19,Fabout the status of the probation
OL,20,Fperiod - if a person cannot be sacked
OL,21,Fmore easily.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
