OL,11,FIt is a package that will be warmly
OL,12,Fwelcomed by most trade unions
OL,13,Faffiliated with Labour, especially
OL,14,Fthose closer to the leadership,
OL,15,Fdespite the two-year delay in
OL,16,Fimplementation.
